task.summary: Default task
Added SqlBuilderFactory class, added sqlBuilder field to SelectStatement class, started writing methods in DbConnectionImpl to get database meta data.
Refining Criteria and Statement classes. Need to refactor other classes that are affected by these changes.
Working on adding parenthesis to criteria.
Working on adding multiple ending parenthesis to criteria.
Testing adding parenthesis to criteria.
Started testing SqlBuilder classes.
SqlBuilderTest and StatementTest tests pass successfully.
Added more tests to QueryTests
Added first draft of SQL Statement randomization tests.
Improved randomized SQL Statement tests.
Randomized SQL Statement tests are passing.
Starting to refine tests.
Removed sub-directory that contained copy of project. Not sure how it got there.
Added SqlBuilder as a field in the SelectStatement class. Deleted abstract Statement class - I did not think it was needed since this is just a library for SELECT statements only.
Changed the SelectStatement's criteria field to be an ArrayList instead of TreeSet so that it works with Spring better.
Added getters and setters for remaining Criteria fields so that Spring can bind request attributes to controller parameters.
Moved logic to sort criteria, clear parenthesis from criteria, and add parenthesis to criteria from setCriteria() to toString() in the SelectStatement class.
Added logic to set a criteria's filter to null if the operator is isNull or isNotNull.
Added logic to set a criteria's filter to null if the operator is isNull or isNotNull.

Changed the SelectStatement's toString method to return a string detailing the object properties. Added toSql method to SelectStatement to build SQL from object. Changed SelectStatement's tableSchema field to a Map instead of ResultSet to reduce object size and make traversing the items of the field possible in SQLite. Added ResultSetToHashMapConverter class for convenience of converting ResultSet objects to Maps.
Added more robust checks in SqlCleanser class. Changed SelectStatement's toString method. Ran randomized SQL tests twice for Postgres, MySQL, and SQLite.
Added regular expression to SqlCleanser class to catch ANSI keywords. Added SqlCleanserTest class.
Removed '%' and 'AND' from SqlCleanser. Added ',' as the join character when joining strings together in wrapFilterInQuotes method.
Refactored how tableSchemas are retrieved - they are now retrieved in the SqlBuilder constructor. Refactored dynamic tests. SQLite dynamic tests are passing.
SQLite and PostgreSQL tests are now passing.
Refactored SqlBuilder constructor to test that the columns in a the SelectStatement's columns and criteria fields can be found in the target database. Tests pass SQLite, MySQL, and PostgreSQL.

Set SelectStatement's databaseType field in the toSql() method using the properties parameter. Removed Types.DATALINK from SqlBuilder typeMappings. Added canParseNonQuotedFilter() method. Tests pass SQLite, MySQL, and PostgreSQL.
